@360CP has spent nearly three decades investing from Paris and Milan across Deep Tech, Climate Tech, and Digital-First markets, managing about €700M and backing founders from pre-seed through Series B across robotics,", "id_str": "2079268868430659616", "is_quote_status": false, "lang": "en", "quote_count": 0, "reply_count": 2, "retweet_count": 1, "retweeted": false, "user_id_str": "231279208"}, "note_tweet": {"is_expandable": true, "note_tweet_results": {"result": {"entity_set": {"hashtags": [{"indices": [613, 628], "text": "VentureCapital"}, {"indices": [629, 638], "text": "DeepTech"}, {"indices": [639, 651], "text": "ClimateTech"}, {"indices": [652, 669], "text": "EuropeanStartups"}, {"indices": [670, 681], "text": "Innovation"}], "symbols": [], "urls": [], "user_mentions": [{"id_str": "115668530", "indices": [60, 66], "name": "360 Capital", "screen_name": "360CP"}]}, "id": "Tm90ZVR3ZWV0OjIwNzkyNjg4NjgzMDkwMzI5NjE=", "text": "European deep tech is not built on startup speedrun logic.

@360CP has spent nearly three decades investing from Paris and Milan across Deep Tech, Climate Tech, and Digital-First markets, managing about €700M and backing founders from pre-seed through Series B across robotics, energy infrastructure, cybersecurity, photonics, advanced sensing, industrial technology, and university spinouts.

